Notes on item iteractions:
General:
- Headshot multiplier is 2x;

Vitality:
- Percentage health increases only affect BASE health;
- All additive health increases are just "Bonus Health";
Weapon:
- Always percentage based(just add percentages and apply at the end);
Spirit:
- Always additive;